            <span id="ctl00_ContentPlaceHolder1_lblTitle" class="title">Ouro ou Bitcoin - o que virá no futuro?<br></span>
            <div style="color:#AAAAAA;padding-top: 10px;padding-bottom: 10px; font-size: 9pt; font-weight: normal;">
                por <a href='SearchByAuthor.aspx?id=293&type=articles' class='articleAuthor'>Detlev Schlichter</a>, quinta-feira, 19 de julho de 2012
            </div>
            
            <hr style="border: 1px dotted #DEDEDE" />
            
            <div style="width: 90%; height: 25px; clear: both; margin-top: 3px;">
            
